    <div class="main review-item" id="5788633">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5788633/" class="title-link">义宁而后称祭酒</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5788633"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/68759687/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u68759687-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/68759687/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Edmund</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-02-23"
      class="main-meta">2013-02-23 01:10:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5788633_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  现已出了唐先生的全集，这部书仍有它的价值。一位治魏晋隋唐史的名学者说过，他当学生的时候把唐先生的论文集都翻烂了。既然做学问要这么做，那这部书再适合不过了。精装、纸厚、色泽微黄，手感极佳，读来有味，就奔着翻烂了去吧。 另外，这部书的编选者是唐先生的弟子和再传，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5788633/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5788633_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5788633_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





